  <div class="panel-body">
    <p>What We Do:</p>
    <li class="list-group-item">We are a product launch and start-up consultancy.  We have the knowledge and the resources to make your ideas into real products.  Our stepped programs offer the flexability to get your products off the ground.  Whether you've got just a sketch, some scribbles or just a notion, we can move you toward the process of bringing your dreams to life.</li>
    <li class="list-group-item">Anything is possible with our network of experts.  From Illustrators and 3d Artists, Web Developers and Graphic Designers, Patent Attorneys and Product Marketers, Engineers and Prototype Designers.  We can offer you short or long term goals with realistic expectations. And these aren't just outside companies we Google and then hire.  We've worked with them throughout the years and we know what they can do.  Design Monster's resources are a network of collaberators and made up of passionate people.</li>
    <li class="list-group-item">We offer product development for all stages.  If one of our packages doesn't quite fit, {{#link-to 'contact'}}CONTACT US{{/link-to}}!  We'll customize a product launch that fits your needs.</li>
